---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="A bit about me and this blog."
	pubDate={new Date('Jun 08 2026')}
>
	<p>
		Hi, and welcome. This is a small personal blog where I write up things I am
		working on and thinking about — notes, projects, and the occasional longer
		piece.
	</p>

	<p>
		The site is a static build made with Astro and written entirely in Markdown,
		so posts stay simple and the pages load fast. Thanks for stopping by.
	</p>
</Layout>
